インタフェースの使用
org.interledger.ilp.InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode

  • InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCodeを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.interledger.ilp
    This package contains classes related to the core Interledger Protocol (ILP) which is the foundational protocol in the overall Interledger suite of protocols.

    • org.interledger.ilpでのInterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCodeの使用

      InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCodeとして宣言されているorg.interledger.ilpのフィールド 
      修飾子とタイプ フィールドと説明
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.F00_BAD_REQUEST
      Generic sender error.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.F01_INVALID_PACKET
      The ILP packet was syntactically invalid.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.F02_UNREACHABLE
      There was no way to forward the payment, because the destination ILP address was wrong or the connector does not have a route to the destination.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.F03_INVALID_AMOUNT
      The amount is invalid, for example it contains more digits of precision than are available on the destination ledger or the amount is greater than the total amount of the given asset in existence.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.F04_INSUFFICIENT_DST_AMOUNT
      The receiver deemed the amount insufficient, for example you tried to pay a $100 invoice with $10.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.F05_WRONG_CONDITION
      The receiver generated a different condition and cannot fulfill the payment.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.F06_UNEXPECTED_PAYMENT
      The receiver was not expecting a payment like this = ErrorCode.of(the memo and destination address don't make sense in that combination, for example if the receiver does not understand the transport protocol used)
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.F07_CANNOT_RECEIVE
      The receiver is unable to accept this payment due to a constraint.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.F99_APPLICATION_ERROR
      Reserved for application layer protocols.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.R00_TRANSFER_TIMED_OUT
      The transfer timed out, meaning the next party in the chain did not respond.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.R01_INSUFFICIENT_SOURCE_AMOUNT
      Either the sender did not send enough money or the exchange rate changed before the payment was prepared.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.R02_INSUFFICIENT_TIMEOUT
      The connector could not forward the payment, because the timeout was too low to subtract its safety margin.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.R99_APPLICATION_ERROR
      Reserved for application layer protocols.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.T00_INTERNAL_ERROR
      A generic unexpected exception.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.T01_LEDGER_UNREACHABLE
      The connector has a route or partial route to the destination but was unable to reach the next ledger.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.T02_LEDGER_BUSY
      The ledger is rejecting requests due to overloading.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.T03_CONNECTOR_BUSY
      The connector is rejecting requests due to overloading.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.T04_INSUFFICIENT_LIQUIDITY
      The connector would like to fulfill your request, but it doesn't currently have enough money.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.T05_RATE_LIMITED
      The sender is sending too many payments and is being rate-limited by a ledger or connector.
      static InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode InterledgerProtocolError.ErrorCode.T99_APPLICATION_ERROR
      Reserved for application layer protocols.
